def_cn: 站不住脚的;无可辩解的
def_en: If you say that a statement, action, or idea is indefensible, you mean that it cannot be justified or supported because it is completely wrong or unacceptable.

def_cn: 无法防御的;无法保卫的
def_en: Places or buildings that are indefensible cannot be defended if they are attacked.
